        "content": "**What the metrics mean:**  \n- *512B* \u2192 Size of the value used in SET/GET operations (in Bytes).\n- *IO* \u2192 Number I/O threads used by `valkey-server`  \n- *P* \u2192 Pipeline level (number of requests grouped into one network round-trip).\n\n**Hardware:**  \n- AWS `c8g.metal-48xl` bare metal instance  \n- NUMA-separated: server and client pinned to different NUMA nodes  \n- Network IRQs isolated away from server CPU cores  \n- Valkey server pinned to dedicated CPU cores  ",
